            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 246,
                    "pathId": -9070989930420754962
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": 1042749670461312938
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4903061798116452801,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女は今日初めて本当の悔しさを知った。\n周囲の声ばかり気にして、\n自分の心の声を聞けていなかったのだ。",
            "enText": "Today, for the first time, she learned of her \ntrue frustration. She had been so concerned \nabout the voices of those around her that \nshe had not been listening to her own heart.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 3382716251254890582
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": 4668406388768016361
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4164764982962895130,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "だが今は、純粋にレースに勝ちたい、\nもっと走りたいと心臓が叫んでいると話す。",
            "enText": "But now, she says, her heart is screaming to \nwin races and run more.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
