            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女の走りに、マネージャーも涙を流した。\n自ら望んだ場所で心から楽しみ、輝く様を\n美しいと賞賛。走ることを認めたのだった。",
            "enText": "Her running brought tears to the manager's \neyes. She praised the beauty of her \nsparkle, enjoying herself in the place she \nwanted to be. She was allowed to run.",
